This page/blog is built to help me organize my ideas and knowledge. If by some chance
it helps someone, great!

> Remember kids. The only difference between screwing around and science is
> writing it down.
>
> Adam Savage.

The topics I am going to talk about are mainly in the field of computer science
and programming. I am specially interested in InfoSec so most of the post will
be on that topic.

